cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CR 

This paper is about fairness-aware ranking in search and recommendation systems, which is a topic that falls under information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses algorithms for computing fairness-aware re-ranking of results, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques, making it relevant to cybernetics (cs.CY) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes measures for quantifying bias, which is related to social and information sciences (cs.SI) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
